{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"componentwillunmount-里面销毁一些\"><a href=\"#componentwillunmount-%E9%87%8C%E9%9D%A2%E9%94%80%E6%AF%81%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>componentWillUnmount() 里面销毁一些</h2>\n<p>we would want to unregister any global/system/library events, destroy 3rd party UI library elements, etc.</p>\n<h2 id=\"多使用-shouldcomponentupdate\"><a href=\"#%E5%A4%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-shouldcomponentupdate\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>多使用 shouldComponentUpdate</h2>\n<p>在其里面必须进行判断,不必要的render坚决不要,(特别是数据问空的情况)这要也能让你梳理清楚页面逻辑</p>\n<h2 id=\"在constructor-bind-this\"><a href=\"#%E5%9C%A8constructor-bind-this\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>在constructor bind this</h2>\n<p>避免不必要的重新编订this</p>\n<h2 id=\"在reducer过滤数据，逻辑在这里尽量抽离，尽可能在组件层面使用无状态组件\"><a href=\"#%E5%9C%A8reducer%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E5%9C%A8%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E6%8A%BD%E7%A6%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%BD%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%9C%A8%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E5%B1%82%E9%9D%A2%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%97%A0%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>在reducer过滤数据，逻辑在这里尽量抽离，尽可能在组件层面使用无状态组件</h2>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"componentWillUnmount() 里面销毁一些 we would want to unregister any global/system/library events, destroy 3rd party UI library elements, etc…","frontmatter":{"title":"react","cover":null,"date":"2017-02-15T10:08:29.000Z","category":"react","tags":["react"]},"fields":{"nextTitle":"keyboard","nextSlug":"/javascript/keybord/","prevTitle":"js作用域与块级作用域","prevSlug":"/javascript/js-domain/","slug":"/react/react-performance-optimization/","date":"2017-02-14T16:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/react/react-performance-optimization/"}}